TITLE: Updating Linter Configuration from ESLintRC to Flat Config Format in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to update the Linter configuration from the old eslintrc format to the new flat config format. It shows the change in structure for specifying parser options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/use/migrate-to-9.0.0.md#2025-04-14_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// eslintrc config format
linter.verify(code, {
	parserOptions: {
		ecmaVersion: 6,
	},
});

// flat config format
linter.verify(code, {
	languageOptions: {
		ecmaVersion: 6,
	},
});
```

