TITLE: Applying a Predefined Configuration Object with Custom Overrides in ESLint
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to import the recommended JavaScript rules configuration and combine it with custom rule settings. The predefined configuration is applied first, followed by an object that overrides the severity of the no-unused-vars rule.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/use/configure/combine-configs.md#2025-04-14_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
