TITLE: Using a Shareable Configuration Package in ESLint (JavaScript)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use a shareable configuration package in an ESLint configuration file. The example imports a configuration and extends it while modifying a rule.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/use/configure/configuration-files.md#2025-04-14_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// eslint.config.js
