TITLE: Fixed Race Condition Using Intermediate Variable
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to fix the race condition by storing the async result in a local variable before updating the shared state.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/rules/require-atomic-updates.md#2025-04-14_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
async function addLengthOfSinglePage(pageNum) {
  const lengthOfThisPage = await getPageLength(pageNum);

  totalLength += lengthOfThisPage;
}
```

