LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
async function retryUpTo10Times() {
    for (let i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
        const wasSuccessful = await tryToDoSomething();
        if (wasSuccessful)
            return 'succeeded!';
        // wait to try again.
        await new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 1000));
    }
    return 'failed!';
}
```

