TITLE: Results Output Handler
DESCRIPTION: Function to process and display ESLint results, counting errors and warnings.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/integrate/integration-tutorial.md#2025-04-14_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function outputLintingResults(results) {
	// Identify the number of problems found
	const problems = results.reduce(
		(acc, result) => acc + result.errorCount + result.warningCount,
		0,
	);

	if (problems > 0) {
		console.log("Linting errors found!");
		console.log(results);
	} else {
		console.log("No linting errors found.");
	}
	return results;
}
```

