TITLE: Demonstrating Correct Object Property Ordering in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Examples showing correct property ordering in objects according to the sort-keys rule. This includes alphabetically sorted properties, proper handling of case sensitivity, non-natural ordering, computed properties, and spread operators.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/rules/sort-keys.md#2025-04-14_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
