TITLE: Extending Fix Range in context.report() in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to extend the range of a fix to prevent other rules from making changes in the same scope.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/extend/custom-rules.md#2025-04-14_snippet_9

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
context.report({
	node,
	message,
	*fix(fixer) {
		yield fixer.replaceText(node, replacementText);

		// extend range of the fix to the range of `node.parent`
		yield fixer.insertTextBefore(node.parent, "");
		yield fixer.insertTextAfter(node.parent, "");
	},
});
```

