SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/use/migrating-to-3.0.0.md#2025-04-14_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
	"extends": "eslint:recommended",
	"rules": {
		"no-unsafe-finally": "off",
		"no-native-reassign": "off",
		"complexity": ["off", 11],
		"comma-dangle": "error",
		"require-yield": "error"
	}
}
```

