TITLE: Enabling Feature Flags with ESLint API
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to enable feature flags when using ESLint's JavaScript API with both the ESLint and Linter classes. The example shows how to pass multiple flags in an array to the constructor options.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/pages/flags.md#2025-04-14_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const { ESLint, Linter } = require("eslint");

const eslint = new ESLint({
	flags: ["flag_one", "flag_two"],
});

const linter = new Linter({
	flags: ["flag_one", "flag_two"],
});
```

