TITLE: ESLint Configuration File
DESCRIPTION: An ESLint configuration file in JSON format that extends the recommended ruleset and adds custom rules for consistent returns, indentation, no-else-return, semicolons, and space around unary operators.
SOURCE: https://github.com/eslint/eslint/blob/main/docs/src/use/formatters/index.md#2025-04-14_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "extends": "eslint:recommended",
    "rules": {
        "consistent-return": 2,
        "indent"           : [1, 4],
        "no-else-return"   : 1,
        "semi"             : [1, "always"],
        "space-unary-ops"  : 2
    }
}
```

